(482, 5, '2019-03-02 15:06:38', '2019-03-02 09:36:38', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our idea is to give a solution for a better education to the unprivileged children of the society. Bodhaan program is to provide an opportunity to individuals to serve as tutors to children from unprivileged communities. The tutors belong to the educated part of the society contributing to a better tomorrow. The interested volunteers can register in the system as instructors to children. This program is to make the kids from under resourced areas be reachable to the education. The system serves as a bridge between the volunteers and the organization for a good cause of providing education to kids from slums and small-budget schools.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2019-03-02 15:06:39', '2019-03-02 09:36:39', '', 7, 'https://electronicsprojectshub.com/bodhaan/?page_id=482', 0, 'page', '', 0),
